    <header>
      <div class="container">
        <h1>CHAT - CODINGON</h1>
        <h2>재치있는 닉네임으로 자신을 소개해보세요!!</h2>
        <div class="entry-box">
          <input type="text" id="nickname" placeholder="Nickname" autofocus style="background-color: #1b62b9; border-radius: 30px; width: 200px; height: 60px; font-size: 20px; color: white; font-style: italic;"/>
          <button type="button" onclick="entry();" onkeypress="if(window.event.keyCode==13){entry()}" style="background-color: #e63838; border-radius: 30px; width: 200px; height: 60px;" >
            <h4 style="font-size: 30px;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 13px;
            padding: 0 0 1rem;
            color: var(--color-white);
            font-style: italic;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            white-space: pre-wrap;">입장하기</h4>
          </button>
        </div>
        <br>
        <br>
        <br>
    
        <div class="chat-box d-none">
          <div id="chat-list" class="chat-list" >
            
          </div>
          <br>
          <select id="nick-list" style="background-color: #ff8400; border-radius: 30px; width: 200px; height: 60px; font-size: 20px; color: white; font-style: italic; text-align: center;"></select
          >
         
         
          <input type="text" id="message" placeholder="전송할 내용을 입력하세요" autofocus onkeypress="if(window.event.keyCode==13){send()}" style="background-color: #d1d0cb; border-radius: 30px; width: 550px; height: 60px; font-size: 20px; color: white; font-style: italic;"/>
          <button type="button" onclick="send();" style="background-color: #a22929; border-radius: 30px; width: 200px; height: 60px;" >
            <h4 style="font-size: 30px;
            position: relative;
            margin-top: 13px;
            padding: 0 0 1rem;
            color: var(--color-white);
            font-style: italic;
            letter-spacing: -0.05em;
            white-space: pre-wrap;">전송하기</h4>
          </button>
          <br>
          <br>
          <a href="/" class="link-github" 
        ><span
          ><svg
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 32 32"
